_sText:
This map is made by: The Wormhole Studios 2009

If you want to know how it looks like - see the pictures!

To install - read the "install.txt" included in the rar-file!

Extra things in the map:
- After 1,5 min you can here some country music in the office area
- L4D box
- L4D poster
- Johnny Cash poster
- Test screen on the TV monitor

I saw the feedback by "CptDobey" and I am now trying to solve the problems, and when you start the map you will get a error "The nav file was created using a different map" (or something); this is just that I built the cubemaps after creating the NAV. So it's noting to worry about.
